function FAQs() { return (

Frequently Asked Questions

What is your app all about?

I love Bonsai plants and I like to share them with the world!

Do you own all these bonsai plants?

Not all of them, but I have a growing collection of my own.

What if I want to suggest a new bosnai to add to your collection?

I would love that! Just click on "Add a Bonsai" above and send me a suggestion!

How can I get in touch with you?

Click the "Contact Me" link above!

); } export default FAQs;
